---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Experience - Julia Kang" description="Explore Julia Kang's professional experience including research positions, development work, and leadership roles.">
	<section class="experience-hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1 class="page-title">Professional Experience</h1>
			<p class="page-subtitle">
				A list of my experiences through research, development, and leadership across biomedical research, AI applications, and software engineering.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="timeline">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="timeline-container">
				<div class="timeline-headers">
					<span class="timeline-header-left">Technical</span>
					<span class="timeline-header-right">Leadership</span>
				</div>
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">Mead Johnson x The Data Mine</h3>
							<span class="duration">Aug 2025 – Present</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Undergraduate Researcher / Developer</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li>Collaborated with Mead Johnson in a multidisciplinary team to design and implement a <strong>Python-based peptide database + Next.js web app</strong> for biomedical research applications</li>
							<li>Identified and integrated data from multiple <strong>open-source peptide databases</strong>, consolidating structural, biochemical, and trait-specific characteristics into a centralized resource</li>
							<li>Designed database infrastructure initially using <strong>PostgreSQL</strong>, then migrated to <strong>SQLite</strong> for improved portability and deployment</li>
							<li>Developed a <strong>React web application</strong> enabling Mead Johnson researchers to search and query peptides relevant to their biomedical research and view relevant data visualizations</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="tech-stack">
							<span class="tech">Python</span>
							<span class="tech">React.js</span>
							<span class="tech">Next.js</span>
							<span class="tech">SQLite</span>
							<span class="tech">PostgreSQL</span>
							<span class="tech">Data Processing</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">Society of Asian Scientists and Engineers (SASE)</h3>
							<span class="duration">Sep 2024 – Present</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Secretary, Admin</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li>Partnered with president and department leads on <strong>long-term strategic vision</strong> of the 350+ member organization</li>
							<li>Managed weekly communications, documented key decisions at board meetings, oversaw event preparation</li>
							<li>Facilitated coordination between different departments and committees to ensure smooth operations</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="impact-stats">
							<div class="stat">
								<span class="stat-number">350+</span>
								<span class="stat-label">Members</span>
							</div>
							<div class="stat">
								<span class="stat-number">Weekly</span>
								<span class="stat-label">Communications</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">Hack the Future</h3>
							<span class="duration">Oct 2025 – Present</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Developer</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li>Collaborating with team members to develop technology solutions for <strong>Sheltering Wings</strong>, a domestic violence support nonprofit organization</li>
							<li>Working on web development projects to support the organization's mission and enhance their digital presence and educational impact</li>
							<li>Applying software engineering skills to create meaningful impact for community-focused nonprofit work</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="tech-stack">
							<span class="tech">Web Development</span>
							<span class="tech">Nonprofit Tech</span>
							<span class="tech">Team Collaboration</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">Boilerexams</h3>
							<span class="duration">Jul 2025 – Present</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Relations Team Member</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li>Communicate with Purdue professors through <strong>in-person meetings, emails, and scheduled appointments</strong> to onboard course materials onto the platform</li>
							<li>Build and maintain <strong>positive relationships with faculty</strong> to ensure continued support and collaboration for Boilerexams</li>
							<li>Lead <strong>tabling events on campus</strong> to advertise and promote the free study resource to students</li>
							<li>Attend <strong>weekly relations team meetings</strong> to coordinate outreach efforts and share progress on faculty communications</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="impact-stats">
							<div class="stat">
								<span class="stat-number">23</span>
								<span class="stat-label">Supported Courses</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">AI for Disaster Response - Purdue VIP</h3>
							<span class="duration">Aug 2025 – Dec 2025</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Undergraduate Researcher / Developer</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li>Conducted research with faculty and peers on applying <strong>AI techniques to disaster response</strong>, focusing on disaster image classification models using <strong>PyTorch</strong></li>
							<li>Implemented and compared multiple ML approaches including <strong>Decision Tree, Random Forest, and CNN models</strong> for disaster image classification</li>
							<li>Applied <strong>HOG and CLIP feature extraction</strong> techniques to enhance model performance and analyze image characteristics</li>
							<li>Synthesized academic literature on AI for disaster detection, damage assessment, and emergency response in weekly research meetings to present findings and refine methodologies</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="tech-stack">
							<span class="tech">PyTorch</span>
							<span class="tech">CNN</span>
							<span class="tech">Random Forest</span>
							<span class="tech">Decision Tree</span>
							<span class="tech">HOG</span>
							<span class="tech">CLIP</span>
							<span class="tech">Computer Vision</span>
							<span class="tech">Disaster Response AI</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">Purdue Taekwondo Club</h3>
							<span class="duration">Apr 2025 – Dec 2025</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Demo Instructor</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li>Led and instructed <strong>2 demonstration team classes every week</strong>, teaching advanced techniques and choreography for public performances</li>
							<li>Mentored team members in martial arts skills, performance techniques, and team coordination</li>
							<li>Contributed to the club's community outreach efforts through dynamic taekwondo demonstrations at university and community events</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">BucketList</h3>
							<span class="duration">Sep 2024 – Jun 2025</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Developer</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li><strong>$1,000 commissioned</strong> goal-focused community platform app for client business inquiry with Purdue ACM SIGAPP</li>
							<li>Created the <strong>Community Board page</strong> using React Native and connected it to AWS backend using Prisma and NodeJS for the backend</li>
							<li>Delivered a scalable mobile application that enables users to create, share, and track personal and community goals</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="tech-stack">
							<span class="tech">React Native</span>
							<span class="tech">AWS</span>
							<span class="tech">Prisma</span>
							<span class="tech">Node.js</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">United Computations</h3>
							<span class="duration">May 2023 – May 2024</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">President, Lead Organizer</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li>Coordinated weekly club meetings and activities promoting various computing topics</li>
							<li>Organized a <strong>24-hour in-person student hackathon (GunnHaX 10.0) with 150+ attendees</strong>, partnering with Major League Hacking (<a href="https://10.0.gunnhacks.com/" target="_blank" class="link">10.0.gunnhacks.com</a>)</li>
							<li>Secured sponsorships from tech companies including Jane Street, Hudson River Trading, and Wolfram to provide prizes and resources</li>
							<li>Raised $250 through a bake sale, managed logistics and teacher shifts, and hosted an AI/ML workshop for attendees</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="impact-stats">
							<div class="stat">
								<span class="stat-number">150+</span>
								<span class="stat-label">Hackathon Attendees</span>
							</div>
							<div class="stat">
								<span class="stat-number">24hr</span>
								<span class="stat-label">Event Duration</span>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">Gunn Computer Science Capstone</h3>
							<span class="duration">Dec 2022 – May 2024</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Student Lead</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li>Deployed <strong>alumni networking NextJS-TypeScript web app</strong> with Supabase SQL database hosted on Netlify (<a href="https://alumni.gunnhigh.school" target="_blank" class="link">alumni.gunnhigh.school</a>)</li>
							<li><strong>Delegated tasks and coordinated meetings</strong> for development and discussed features with 40+ community members</li>
							<li>Led a student team in creating a platform that connects current students with alumni for mentorship and career guidance</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="tech-stack">
							<span class="tech">Next.js</span>
							<span class="tech">TypeScript</span>
							<span class="tech">Supabase</span>
							<span class="tech">Leadership</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">Inspirogram with E3Empower</h3>
							<span class="duration">Jan 2022 – Aug 2022</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Course Developer, Lead Teacher</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li>Launched curricula to teach <strong>HTML/CSS/JS and React.js</strong> for Arusha Girls Secondary School in Tanzania</li>
							<li>Constructed <strong>interactive lessons, code-along videos, and virtual live sessions</strong> for teaching</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="tech-stack">
							<span class="tech">HTML</span>
							<span class="tech">CSS</span>
							<span class="tech">JavaScript</span>
							<span class="tech">React.js</span>
							<span class="tech">Curriculum Development</span>
							<span class="tech">Teaching</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="pitch-competitions">
		<div class="container">
			<h2 class="section-title">Pitch Competitions</h2>
			<div class="competitions-grid">
				<div class="competition-card">
					<div class="competition-header">
						<img src="/mec_logo.jpeg" alt="Model Entrepreneur Competition" class="competition-logo" />
						<h3 class="competition-name">2023 Model Entrepreneur Competition</h3>
						<span class="competition-date"></span>
					</div>
					<h4 class="competition-result">Finalist</h4>
					<ul class="competition-details">
						<li>Peace of Mind</li>
						<li>One of ~60 teams to move on to final round</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="competition-card">
					<div class="competition-header">
						<img src="/conrad_challenge_logo.jpg" alt="Conrad Challenge" class="competition-logo" />
						<h3 class="competition-name">2023 Conrad Challenge</h3>
						<span class="competition-date"></span>
					</div>
					<h4 class="competition-result">Conrad Innovator</h4>
					<ul class="competition-details">
						<li>Peace of Mind</li>
						<li>One of ~200 teams awarded Conrad Innovator under Health & Nutrition category</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				<div class="competition-card">
					<div class="competition-header">
						<img src="/diamond_challenge_logo.jpeg" alt="Diamond Challenge" class="competition-logo" />
						<h3 class="competition-name">2021 Diamond Challenge</h3>
						<span class="competition-date">Sep 2020 - Apr 2021</span>
					</div>
					<h4 class="competition-result">Participant</h4>
					<ul class="competition-details">
						<li>FalconUp Investment</li>
						<li>Selected to move onto Live Pitching round</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="skills-used">
		<div class="container">
			<h2 class="section-title">Key Skills Demonstrated</h2>
			<div class="skills-showcase">
				<div class="skill-group">
					<h3>Technical Skills</h3>
					<div class="skill-list">
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Python Development & Data Processing</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Machine Learning with PyTorch</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Mobile App Development (React Native)</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Full-Stack Web Development</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Cloud Infrastructure (AWS)</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="skill-group">
					<h3>Leadership & Soft Skills</h3>
					<div class="skill-list">
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Team Leadership & Project Management</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Strategic Planning & Vision</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Stakeholder Communication</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Research & Analysis</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Cross-functional Collaboration</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.experience-hero {
		padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
		background: #fafaf8;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 1000px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.page-title {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.page-subtitle {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: #6a6a6a;
		max-width: 700px;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.timeline {
		padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
		background: #fafaf8;
	}

	.timeline-container {
		position: relative;
		max-width: 800px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.timeline-headers {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		padding: 0 40px;
	}

	.timeline-header-left,
	.timeline-header-right {
		font-size: 1.15rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #5372aa;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
	}

	.timeline-header-left {
		margin-left: -28px;
	}

	.timeline-header-right {
		margin-right: -32px;
	}

	.timeline-container::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 10px;
		top: 2rem;
		bottom: 0;
		width: 2px;
		background: #a9b4cd;
	}

	.timeline-container::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		right: 10px;
		top: 2rem;
		bottom: 0;
		width: 2px;
		background: #a9b4cd;
	}

	.timeline-item {
		position: relative;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		padding-left: 40px;
		padding-right: 40px;
	}

	.timeline-item::after {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		right: 5px;
		top: 8px;
		width: 8px;
		height: 8px;
		background: #5372aa;
		border: 2px solid #fafaf8;
		border-radius: 50%;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.timeline-marker {
		position: absolute;
		left: 5px;
		top: 8px;
		width: 12px;
		height: 12px;
		background: #5372aa;
		border: 2px solid #fafaf8;
		border-radius: 50%;
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.timeline-content {
		background: transparent;
		border: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
	}

	.timeline-content:hover {
		border-color: #a9b4cd;
	}

	.timeline-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: flex-start;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
	}

